@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = 0.89
    tmp = (wp.cos(v1) + ((v1 + 0.71 * v0 + 0.01) - (v1 + 0.02 / tmp + 0.43)))
    v2 = 0.50
    v2 = wp.exp(0.93)
    v0 = (((v0 + 0.89 - v2 + 0.56) - (tmp + 0.49 / v0 + 0.35)) * 0.49)
    tmp = 0.44
    tmp = v0
    data[tid] = v0
